h1. Monoku Selecta

By David Avellaneda & John Acosta [Monoku]

Monoku Selecta is a Mootools based select extension, it creates a wrapper and let you style the select element. We hated the mooselecta, so we did this one :)

h2. Usage

Just Use the MonokuSelecta class with your selector:  
@new MonokuSelecta(".my-selector");@

